sequenceDiagram
    participant Architect
    participant gcloud_search as arckit.gcloud-search
    participant gcloud_clarify as arckit.gcloud-clarify
    participant evaluate as arckit.evaluate
    participant Supplier
    
    Architect->>gcloud_search: Search G-Cloud 14 catalogue
    gcloud_search->>gcloud_search: WebSearch Digital Marketplace
    gcloud_search->>Architect: ARC-{PID}-GCS-v{VER}.md<br/>(shortlist 3-5 services)
    
    Architect->>gcloud_clarify: Validate service descriptions
    gcloud_clarify->>gcloud_clarify: Gap analysis (MUST/SHOULD)
    gcloud_clarify->>Architect: ARC-{PID}-GCCL-v{VER}.md<br/>(prioritized questions)
    
    Architect->>Supplier: Send clarification questions
    Supplier->>Architect: Responses + evidence
    
    Architect->>evaluate: Score supplier responses
    evaluate->>Architect: ARC-{PID}-EVAL-v{VER}.md<br/>(vendor scorecard)
